data.meta_description:
Hi, 
Im really having some problems with this pair, i simply cant find them. 
 
I have a marriage cert. for a George Gibson and a Eliza Downs dated 1856 Drayton  On the cert. George has parents as father William Gibson occupation Jeweller and mother as Susannah Gibson nee Hutchinson. 
George's death cert. dated 1892 has his age as 62 father is noted as William Gibson occupation Jeweller and this time mother is noted as Jane. It also states George had been in Australia for 52 years. Informant on
